a^{17-1}=a^{16}\equiv 1\pmod{17}
 1024000000002 = 16\cdot64000000000+2 
 4^{1024000000002}=4^{16\cdot64000000000+2}=(4^{16})^{64000000000}(4^2)\equiv(1)(16)\pmod{17} 
4^2=16\equiv-1\pmod {17}
a\equiv b\pmod m\implies a^n\equiv b^n\pmod m
n\ge0,
4^{1024000000002}=(4^2)^{512000000001}\equiv(-1)^{512000000001}\pmod{17}\equiv-1\equiv16
